Our NEW Spaghetti Squash Stir-Fry is a hearty, delicious way to enjoy it! 🤩 Think: squash "noodles" combined with colorful vegetables 🫑🧅, flavorful baked tofu, & the best stir-fry sauce you've ever tried 🥜...& just 10 simple INGREDIENTS to make it! // LINK in bio for the recipe!⁠⁠
⁠⁠
#spaghettisquash #stirfry #easyveganrecipes #vegandinnerideas
